## Architecture

This project uses **React 19 + Vite 6** with file-based routing patterns:

- **src/pages/** — Page components (lazy-loaded by route)
- **src/routes/index.ts** — router definition (createBrowserRouter)
- **src/App.tsx** — Root layout with `<Outlet />`
- **tests/** — Vitest + @testing-library/react

Key conventions:

- Route definitions go in `src/routes/`, pages in `src/pages/`
- Data fetching uses TanStack Query (`useQuery` / `useMutation`)
- All components use standard TypeScript + React patterns
- Tests are co-located in `tests/` matching the `src/` structure
